1.title: Episode #2.1
1.plot: Navya is doing great at her job but her boss is not happy with her. Nandini sends messages to the team mates to inform them about Manik's birthday celebration which puts them in a fix.

2.title: Episode #2.2
2.plot: Manik's birthday celebration is Nandini's attempt to reunite the FAB5. Harshad burns down the bribe offered by Nyonika. Nandini plays a prank in order to make Mukti, Navya and Alya attend the party.

3.title: Episode #2.3
3.plot: The FAB5 is shocked to hear Maddy playing Manik's favourite tune. Next day on the 'Rakshabandhan' festival, Alya doesn't tie the band on Harshad's hand as she's disgusted by his deeds.

4.title: Episode #2.4
4.plot: Agitated with Maddy, Mukti decides to hit him with her bike, Nandini stops her. Mukti and Alya convince Maddy to join them in the jam in session. Maddy manages to dodge them.

5.title: Episode #2.5
5.plot: Harshad and Nandini are announced as the candidates for the President's post. Maddy tries convincing Nyonika to let him contest. Harshad blackmails Nyonika to make him the President.

6.title: Episode #2.6
6.plot: Maddy loses the first competition to Nandini. Mukti takes all her frustration out on little Abeer. Dhruv is ready with a song but is upset with his team mates for not supporting him.

7.title: Episode #2.7
7.plot: Manik, Mukti, and Alya console each other. Navya gives Sahil the permission to spend some time with Abeer. Harshad makes Alya realise her feelings for Varun.

8.title: Episode #2.8
8.plot: Nandini asks Maddy to put cow dung on his face if she wins the elections.

9.title: Episode #2.9
9.plot: Dhruv informs his friends that FAB5 has been banned from O2. Mukti rebels against her owner's conventional thoughts.

10.title: Episode #2.10
10.plot: Harshad deletes Maddy's records from the data room to pull him out of election and Nandini finds his records.

11.title: Episode #2.11
11.plot: The election results are going to be announced in Space Academy, Dhruv wants Alya to motivate him to dance.

12.title: Episode #2.12
12.plot: Nandini tries to reunite the team FAB5 for the Talent Hunt being held in the Academy, but fails. She recalls her passion for music and takes part in the competition.

13.title: Episode #2.13
13.plot: Maddy stops his performance after he notices Ustaad Mukesh; he is invited by Nandini. Maddy torments Nandini by singing Manik's song.

14.title: Episode #2.14
14.plot: Maddy locks Nandini up in the music room and leaves. Her friends rescue her and try really to cheer her up.

15.title: Episode #2.15
15.plot: Nandini figures out that Rishabh is with Maddy and she rushes to Maddy's house. Maddy's song makes Rishabh speak which overwhelms Nandini. The secretary helps Navya and Mukti cure Abeer.

16.title: Episode #2.16
16.plot: Nandini wins the Presidential elections of Space Academy. After much partying, the Fab Five get a note from the society asking them to empty the flat. The next day, Nandini hears Nyonika talking about the Fab Five being warned and not banned.

17.title: Episode #2.17
17.plot: Nandini is informed that FAB5 has been banned by Nyonika. Mukti decides to apply for Abeer's adoption.

18.title: Episode #2.18
18.plot: Navya is upset with Mukti for having posted an advertisement for Abeer's adoption.

19.title: Episode #2.19
19.plot: The cops visit Mukti and Navya for the interrogation related to Abeer. Nandini and Aryaman finds the details of the driver.

20.title: Episode #2.20
20.plot: The driver escapes before Nandini and Aryaman find him. The society chairman saves Mukti and Navya from the cops and nd reminds them that they need to vacate the house.

21.title: Episode #2.21
21.plot: Maddy saves Nandini from an accident, Nyonika threatens Harshad for his involvement. Dhruv explains to his friends that the Band's success was Manik's dream.

22.title: Episode #2.22
22.plot: Nandini is informed that O2 wants FAB5 to perform. Harshad creates misunderstanding between the team mates by accusing Aryaman for the blast.

23.title: Episode #2.23
23.plot: All the evidence are against Aryaman and the teammates have no option but to hold him responsible for the blas.

24.title: Episode #2.24
24.plot: Aryaman finds the driver, who reveals that Nyonika paid him to plant the bomb in the car.

25.title: Episode #2.25
25.plot: Nandini is informed that Nyonika resigned from her post, Aryaman threatens Harshad to stay away from Nandini.

26.title: Episode #2.26
26.plot: Their jam-in session is interrupted by Maddy as he informs them that he has allotted the music room to another team for practice.

27.title: Episode #2.27
27.plot: The FAB5 is not allowed to perform without Manik at the O2 recording. The team decides to find their lead singer and find Maddy having the same voice as Manik.

28.title: Episode #2.28
28.plot: Maddy rejects the offer to become the lead singer of FAB5. Nandini reminds him about his promise to support FAB5.

29.title: Episode #2.29
29.plot: Navya receives a call for Abeer's adoption. Maddy is restless because Nandini called him an imposter. Nandini finds a band that she gifted to Manik.

30.title: Episode #2.30
30.plot: Ustaad Mukesh asks Maddy to join him in the Kerala trip. Navya hosts the upcoming show of FAB5.

31.title: Episode #2.31
31.plot: A guy who looks like Manik is seen listening to FAB5. Maddy is irritated by Ustaad's decision to not let him pursue rock music.

32.title: Episode #2.32
32.plot: Maddy enters when it's the singer's turn in the performance and saves FAB5. Manik returns and is upset to witness Maddy on the stage.

33.title: Episode #2.33
33.plot: Nandini and friends are startled to see Manik playing guitar in the music room, they are ecstatic to see him alive.

34.title: Episode #2.34
34.plot: Maddy taunts his grandfather by telling him about his mind boggling rock music performance. Nandini meets Manik and consoles him.

35.title: Episode #2.35
35.plot: The FAB5 team has finally united. Ustaad Mukesh disowns Maddy because he chose rock music over classical music.

36.title: Episode #2.36
36.plot: Aryaman offers Maddy to stay with him. The FAB5 is celebrating Manik's return and they think about Kabir. Manik is jealous as Aryaman gets close to Nandini.

37.title: Episode #2.37
37.plot: During the game, Aryaman's closeness toward Nadini makes Manik jealous. They sneak out from the group and spend some romantic moments together.

38.title: Episode #2.38
38.plot: Manik dedicates a song to Nandini and tells her that she is his inspiration. Manik decides to fulfill all the wishes from Nandini's bucket list.

39.title: Episode #2.39
39.plot: While Alya, Dhruv, and Mukti are busy discussing their future, Madhyam is approached by a businessman who wants him to sing in one of the upcoming events.

40.title: Episode #2.40
40.plot: Gamath offers a deal to Maddy for his performance with FAB5. Aryaman fears that Maddy might hurt Manik's sentiment by being in FAB5.

41.title: Episode #2.41
41.plot: Sahil and his wife meet Navya regarding Abeer's adoption. Manik is overjoyed to find Rishabh speaking. He is shattered to learn that his friends begged Madhyam to sing for FAB5.

42.title: Episode #2.42
42.plot: Manik comes to know that Maddy is responsible for Steve's recovery. Maddy replaces Manik's position in the band and humiliates him for it. Meanwhile Mukti convinces Navya to give Abhir up for adoption.

43.title: Episode #2.43
43.plot: Madhyam tells Nandini that he will keep an eye on the FAB5. He also accepts the businessman's deal. Navya tests the capability of Sahil and Kiran if they want to adopt Abeer.

44.title: Episode #2.44
44.plot: Maddy accepts the singing contract to target Manik. Later Nandini and Manik come to know about the contract from Dhruv.

45.title: Episode #2.45
45.plot: Harshad wants to become the college President. Mukti convinces Navya to let the couple, Sahil and Kiran stay with them. Maddy sings the song composed by FAB5, in the event.

46.title: Episode #2.46
46.plot: Manik gets angry at Maddy for stealing the FAB5's song and Navya agrees to give her baby up for adoption. Later, Manik and Nandini spend some romantic moments together.

47.title: Episode #2.47
47.plot: Harshad taunts Alya for living her life as guided by Manik and Dhruv. Manik meets with the businessman and entices him into replacing Maddy by FAB5.

48.title: Episode #2.48
48.plot: Bhai questions Alia's passion for music. Meanwhile Manik's influence gets his band the chance to perform at the event.

49.title: Episode #2.49
49.plot: Maddy and Manik have an argument during the jamming session. Agitated Maddy offers a deal to the businessman to let him perform in the concert instead of FAB5.

50.title: Episode #2.50
50.plot: Maddy loses to Manik in the guitar solo challenge. He also offers to perform for free and requests the organizers to cancel their contract with Manik.

51.title: Episode #2.51
51.plot: For his own benefit, the businessman tries to showcase both the performances but unfortunately Maddy and Manik start fighting on the stage.

52.title: Episode #2.52
52.plot: The FAB5 and Maddy have to perform on the same day but only Maddy ends up performing. Maddy and Manik get into a fight and Manik is left unconscious.

53.title: Episode #2.53
53.plot: Manik is brought back home after he faints on the stage. The doctor informs about an internal head injury. Navya and Mukti are enjoying their time with Sahil and Kiran.

54.title: Episode #2.54
54.plot: The Doctor reveals Manik's injury, this makes the FAB5 and Nandini worried. They decide to take revenge on Maddy. Meanwhile Navya checks the capabilities of Abeer's adoptive parents.

55.title: Episode #2.55
55.plot: Everyone wakes up on the Diwali morning thinking about the evening celebration. But some misunderstandings and doubts surround a few relationships.

56.title: Episode #2.56
56.plot: Manik and Nandini revive their love on the occasion of Diwali. Meanwhile Maddy refuses to accept Nandini's apology.

57.title: Episode #2.57
57.plot: Manik finds Nandini talking to Maddy, who is leaving the town. Harshad announces that he's been made the college President and Dhruv is jealous of Alya's boss.

58.title: Episode #2.58
58.plot: Manik and his friends are shocked at seeing Harshad as the new president of Space Academy. Meanwhile Nandini presents Manik his old guitar as a Diwali gift and asks him to complete the song.

59.title: Episode #2.59
59.plot: While everyone is celebrating Diwali, Manik and Nandini find a romantic spot to spend the time together. Harshad provokes Aryaman so much that he reveals his love for Nandini.

60.title: Episode #2.60
60.plot: Manik and Nandini are reliving their happy moments. Meanwhile, Aryaman confesses his love to Nandini.

61.title: Episode #2.61
61.plot: Harshad tries showing his power to Manik. Nandini comes across some news of Maddy. Navya's boss indirectly asks her to compromise to grab the job.

62.title: Episode #2.62
62.plot: Harshad challenges Manik for the upcoming Musicana festival. Harshad taunts him that the FAB5 do not have a drummer after Cabir's death. Harshad suggests that Manik add Aaryaman to his band.

63.title: Episode #2.63
63.plot: Manik is furious at Nandini for showing up late because of Aryaman. Navya is becoming dubious about Sahil and Kiran. FAB5 breaks down while playing Kabir's tune.

64.title: Episode #2.64
64.plot: In spite of them missing their drummer, Manik wants to start practice the next day while Mukti worries about the band breaking up. Meanwhile, Sahil and Kiran act in a suspicious manner towards Navya.

65.title: Episode #2.65
65.plot: Manik fulfills one wish from Nandini's bucket list; they notice Sahil hugging a guy inside a car. The guy is Sahil's boyfriend, but Sahil cleverly lies to them.

66.title: Episode #2.66
66.plot: Manik and Nandini decide to watch a movie in the local theatre to fulfill the bucket list. On their way back, they accidentally spot Sahil.

67.title: Episode #2.67
67.plot: Alya comes across Kiran's audition tape in which she calls herself Raima. Nandini and Manik are already skeptical about Sahil and Kiran. Navya decides to find out the truth.

68.title: Episode #2.68
68.plot: Nandini is restless and Manik tells her to relax. Later, they inform Navya that Sahil is gay and that they are concerned about Abhir's future.

69.title: Episode #2.69
69.plot: Alya comes with Raima's footage to show it to everyone. Manik informs them that Sahil has a boyfriend and Kiran isn't his wife.

70.title: Episode #2.70
70.plot: Manik tries explaining to Nandini about the disease from which he is suffering. Ustaad Mukesh sets up a test in the class which qualifies the students for the competition.

71.title: Episode #2.71
71.plot: Nandini and her friends qualify for the 'Music Gana'. Alya confronts Varun about him cheating on her.

72.title: Episode #2.72
72.plot: Nandini has arranged a party. Aryaman confesses his feelings for Nandini. Nandini tells everyone that Manik is suffering from partial amnesia.

1.title: Episode #1.1
1.plot: Nandini unites two fighting lovers. She fondly collects fireflies believing they're the harbinger of true love. Nandini shifts to Mumbai with Shannoo and Murthy for Rishabh's treatment.

2.title: Episode #1.2
2.plot: Navya reaches Mumbai to learn singing. Kabir takes a gullible Shahid for a ride and posts his naked images online. The shame and humiliation Shahid receives drives him to kill himself.

3.title: Episode #1.3
3.plot: Nandini and Navya intervene and save Shahid's life. This incident draws media attention towards the college. The college offers full scholarships to both of them in order to save it's reputation.

4.title: Episode #1.4
4.plot: Amma Maa implores Nandini to pursue her own dream rather than her father's. This makes Nandini decide to join S.P.A.C.E. where Nandini and Navya meet FAB5 for the first time.

5.title: Episode #1.5
5.plot: Navya can not believe it when she is invited by FAB5. Instead they lock her up in a garbage bin as a revenge for saving Shahid. Shahid tells Nandini about Kabir's video which shows Navya trapped.

6.title: Episode #1.6
6.plot: Nandini saves Navya which enrages the FAB5 even more. This incident stregthens Navya and Nandini's bond. The FAB5 wants Navya to disclose who saved her to be able to join them.

7.title: Episode #1.7
7.plot: Nandini and Navya are shocked at their treatment by FAB5. Niyonika uses Manik to get some papers signed by Manik's father. Nandini unknowingly visit's Manik's house. Manik takes her father's pen.

8.title: Episode #1.8
8.plot: Nandini and Rishabh jump into the pool to recover the pen. When the pen isn't found, Nandini wants it back from the FAB5. They dare Nandini to do what they say to get her father's pen.

9.title: Episode #1.9
9.plot: Nandini hits Manik in an argument. This enrages him. Dhruv asks Manik not to harass Nandini.

10.title: Episode #1.10
10.plot: Navya is in a dilemma as her dreams can only be fulfilled by joining FAB5. That would mean ending her friendship with Nandini. Nandini and Manik perform together on Friendship Day.

11.title: Episode #1.11
11.plot: Manik takes Nandini to FAB5's friendship day party at his house after the performance at the old age home. Nandini seems delighted to be at the party, but she is unaware of what is to happen.

12.title: Episode #1.12
12.plot: Nandini starts breaking expensive artefacts at Manik's place as she is furious with the FAB5 for having upset her. Manik is upset with Nandini as she behaves that way.

13.title: Episode #1.13
13.plot: Manik arrives at Nandini's house. He compels Nandini to sign a contract which will bind her to act as his spot girl. Nandini isn't happy about signing the contract.

14.title: Episode #1.14
14.plot: Manik meets Nandini. He notifies the highlights of the contracts that are the rules which she needs to follow. Nandini feels that Manik is mistreating her.

15.title: Episode #1.15
15.plot: Manik makes Nandini perform a series of chores meant for servants. At Dhruv's place, Nandini notices the star which is also drawn on her brother's bedroom wall.

16.title: Episode #1.16
16.plot: Nandini tries to find out the mystery behind the star's drawing. Rishabh and Manik avoid her. Nandini is suspicious about Rishabh and Manik's behaviour towards her.

17.title: Episode #1.17
17.plot: Manik punishes Nandini compelling her to kiss him. He makes her drink a disgusting mocktail. Dhruv stops Nandini from doing it. Nandini is elated as Dhruv comes to her rescue.

18.title: Episode #1.18
18.plot: Nandini follows Navya's plan to get rid of Manik's torture. Nandini refuses to follow his order. Manik arrives at her place where he notices the star art also to be found at Dhruv's place.

19.title: Episode #1.19
19.plot: Alya calls for a FAB5 emergency meeting where they take her side. Alya compels Manik to end his contract with Nandini. Nandini is thankful to Alya to have freed her from the despicable contract.

20.title: Episode #1.20
20.plot: Harshad, Navya, Nandini, and FAB5 are in the same pool but on the opposite ends. FAB5 leaves no opportunity to trouble Nandini and Navya. Nandini and Navya are irritated.

21.title: Episode #1.21
21.plot: Manik comes to meet Nandini at her place to talk about the connection between Dhruv and her brother. Harshad surprises everyone by announcing Navya and Nandini as his band members.

22.title: Episode #1.22
22.plot: Nandini refuses to be a part of Harshad's band. Alya sets Nandini up by having two goons force themselves on her. Nandini is yet to find out that Alya has sent those goons.

23.title: Episode #1.23
23.plot: Nandini breaks down. She blames Manik for all of her troubles. Dhruv punches Manik in the face when he accepts this. Manik regrets having mistreated Nandini.

24.title: Episode #1.24
24.plot: Harshad messes up with FAB5 and tries breaking them apart. Mukti calls Alya and tells her that she will commit suicide as the FAB5 has separated. Everyone is worried about Mukti's threat.

25.title: Episode #1.25
25.plot: Harshad protests at the college to revoke Nandini's expulsion order. Manik and Nandini are stressed out on Dhruv's absence in the college. Manik and Nandini contemplate what to do next.

26.title: Episode #1.26
26.plot: Harshad compels the FAB5 to leave the practice room. Dhruv spots Alya paying money to the goons for harassing Nandini. Dhruv feels betrayed by Alya, as she hatched a plan against Nandini.

27.title: Episode #1.27
27.plot: Nandini calls for Manik's help when she is unable to handle Dhruv's strange attacks. Harshad learns that Alya is being blackmailed by a person. Harshad is worried about Alya.

28.title: Episode #1.28
28.plot: Nandini informs her uncle and aunt that she has been working in the college cafe. Kabir surprises his gang by introducing his girlfriend to them.

29.title: Episode #1.29
29.plot: Raghav calls for a jamming session for the participative bands. While practising, Nandini and Dhruv sneak out to secretly meet each other. Nandini and Dhruv share a good time.

30.title: Episode #1.30
30.plot: Nandini and Manik get locked in the store room. The goons hired by Alya start harassing her. Manik is worried about Nandini being harassed by the goons.

31.title: Episode #1.31
31.plot: Nandini and Manik are locked in the store room. Their respective band members are worried because of their absence. The band members start looking for Nandini and Manik.

32.title: Episode #1.32
32.plot: Nandini and Manik are locked inside the store room till the night. Navya, Harshad and Alya find them. They notice Manik holding Nandini by her waist. Everyone is shocked.

33.title: Episode #1.33
33.plot: Nandini and Manik are teased for spending their last night together. Raghav punishes the FAB5, Nandini and Navya by asking them to look for their music instruments hidden in a forest.

34.title: Episode #1.34
34.plot: The two bands are engaged in the treasure hunt. Manik and Harshad notice the final treasure. They run for it and accidentally tackle Nandini off the cliff, and chaos ensues.

35.title: Episode #1.35
35.plot: Part one of Raghav's punishment has concluded. Part two consists of the bands performing live that too only with the found instruments. The bands are up for the challenge.

36.title: Episode #1.36
36.plot: Nandini suggests the two bands to perform together as they had no time left to practise and very less instruments. This manages to impress Raghav.

37.title: Episode #1.37
37.plot: Kabir comes up with a plan to unmask Harshad's true face in front of his band. He partially succeeds. But he also ends up losing trust on one of his own band member.

38.title: Episode #1.38
38.plot: Manik feels betrayed as Dhruv and Alya had kept a huge secret from him. Harshad tries to defend himself in front of his band. The band members are not convinced that easily.

39.title: Episode #1.39
39.plot: Manik breaks up with Alya. Dhruv breaks his friendship with Nandini in order to secure his friendship with Manik. Dhruv and Manik try to bond.

40.title: Episode #1.40
40.plot: Raghav makes performing difficult for the band members by asking them to play classical Indian fusion. He also interchanges the members of the two bands.

41.title: Episode #1.41
41.plot: FAB5 continue to bully Nandini. In the process, they end up hurting her. Dhruv turns out to be the only one mature amongst the arrogant five. He and Nandini become good friends.

42.title: Episode #1.42
42.plot: Harshad calls Navya and Nandini to practise for the competition at his house. Alya calls FAB5 to her home to party. Manik wants Alya to stay away from him until the competition is over.

43.title: Episode #1.43
43.plot: Manik overhears Kabir telling Rose to maintain the secret that she's not his girlfriend. Kabir tells the truth. Kabir evades. Both NH3 and FAB5 prepare for a face-off with music.

44.title: Episode #1.44
44.plot: Nandini's last-minute persuation gives Navya the impetus to sing in the competition. Manik vanishes moments before his performance as he had to tend to Rishabh who suffers a panic attack at S.P.A.C.E.

45.title: Episode #1.45
45.plot: Manik stays with Rishabh at the hospital. He performs for FAB5 through his phone. The judges declare NH3 as winners. Dhruv and Manik tide over the minor differences in their friendship.

46.title: Episode #1.46
46.plot: Manik did not forget Kabir's well-kept secret. He asks Kabir to share it. Manik also threatens Nandini to never tell anyone why he couldn't come to the competition. Navya has a crush on Harshad.

47.title: Episode #1.47
47.plot: Manik hides Nandini in his house to avoid his band members discovering her. The band members pour in one by one. Navya is thinking of ways to advance her relation with Harshad.

48.title: Episode #1.48
48.plot: With everyone inside the house, Manik tries to sneak Nandini out of his house. She finally manages to exit after every one has passed out. She suggests Manik they should help Rishabh and Dhruv.

49.title: Episode #1.49
49.plot: Navya tells Nandini she is in love with Harshad. Raghav sir asks all of them to prepare for the upcoming music competition. Manik and Nandini join hands to help Dhruv and Rishabh out.

50.title: Episode #1.50
50.plot: Alya finds that Mukti has started taking drugs again. Manik once again reminds Kabir to talk about his secret to him but he evades it again. Nandini feels attracted to Dhruv but he doesn't reciprocate.

51.title: Episode #1.51
51.plot: Navya starts doubting Dhruv and Manik to be gay after she ovearhears their conversation. She tells Nandini about it. NH3 follows every member of FAB5 at every step to know their planning for Musicana.

52.title: Episode #1.52
52.plot: Nandini tells Manik about Harshad's plan. Manik is shocked to know the truth about Kabir which he had kept secret until now. Manik confronts Kabir who confesses about his sexuality.

53.title: Episode #1.53
53.plot: Kabir tells Raghav that Manik knows about him now. Dhruv tries to learn the signs of true love. Nandini and Manik have found love in each other. Alya decides to get Manik back in her life.

54.title: Episode #1.54
54.plot: Nandini tells Harshad they should stop following FAB5. Alya encourages Dhruv to confess his love to Nandini. Manik and Nandini come closer to each other every passing day.

55.title: Episode #1.55
55.plot: Manik asks Kabir who he is dating. Dhruv tells Manik that he's trying to be friends again with Nandini. This makes Manik feel jealous. Everyone come together and celebrate Raghav's birthday.

56.title: Episode #1.56
56.plot: Kabir and Raghav continue to meet secretly. Alya decides to use Dhruv to get Manik back from Nandini. Mukti cautions Navya about Harshad's real intentions.

57.title: Episode #1.57
57.plot: Alya tutors Dhruv about how to make a girl fall in love with a boy. Nandini can't trace her way back home and stays with Manik. Raghav fears his relation with Kabir will soon be found.

58.title: Episode #1.58
58.plot: Nandini is drunk and tries to kiss Manik who stops her and drops her back home. Harshad guises a woman and meets Navya and lures her with his sweet talk. Mukti is in pain and misses Harshad.

59.title: Episode #1.59
59.plot: Manik teases Nandini by telling her that they got intimate while she was drunk. Manik and gang discover that someone spiked the drinks in the party. Nandini is astounded to learn that Raghav is Kabir's boyfriend.

60.title: Episode #1.60
60.plot: Nandini tells Manik that Kabir's drink was purposely spiked to know his truth. Manik arranges a special Diwali party where he invites all. Alya preps Dhruv to face Nandini in the party.

61.title: Episode #1.61
61.plot: Shahid interrupts as Dhruv is about to confess his feelings to Nandini at the party. Kabir is worried about Raghav. Manik tells Nandini that he and Alya have parted.

62.title: Episode #1.62
62.plot: Mukti hides the fact from Alya that she has resorted to taking drugs. Nandini tells Manik that Kabir and Raghav are a pair. Raghav tells Kabir that they're breaking up.

63.title: Episode #1.63
63.plot: Mukti jumps into another relation to get over Harshad. This makes Alya question herself if she will ever forget Manik. Dhruv gets to know that Nandini has made her place in Manik's heart.

64.title: Episode #1.64
64.plot: Manik is enraged by the fact that Raghav dumped Kabir. Harshad spies on Kabir and comes to know of his relation with Raghav. Alya voices her concern about Mukti's drug abuse to Manik.

65.title: Episode #1.65
65.plot: Kabir thanks Nandini for saving a conflict between Manik and Raghav. She assures that she won't share his secret with anyone. Harshad decides to use Kabir's secret to defame FAB5 before Musicana.

66.title: Episode #1.66
66.plot: Both FAB5 and NH3 put their best feet forward once before Musicana starts. Navya asks Harshad if he really loves her. Dhruv invites Nandini to a special date. She does not know who is behind it.

67.title: Episode #1.67
67.plot: Nandini arrives at Dhruv's special date without knowing it's planned by him. Alya fails to talk Mukti out of her drug abuse. Dhruv is getting ready to meet Nandini in the special setting.

68.title: Episode #1.68
68.plot: Dhruv tells Manik how he feels about Nandini. Kabir and Raghav are filmed by Harshad. Alya loses hope of getting Manik back. The meeting between Dhruv and Nandini fails.

69.title: Episode #1.69
